      <title>伊朗威胁称，如果以色列核设施遭到袭击，将对其发动袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/iran-threatens-strike-on-israeli-nuclear-sites-if-it-s-attacked</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗警告以色列不要攻击其核设施，并威胁称，如果该国的核设施成为攻击目标，伊朗将做出同样的回应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/iran-threatens-strike-on-israeli-nuclear-sites-if-it-s-attacked</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 13:08:41 GMT</pubDate>
